    format("A region steeped in mythology and ancient lore.\pIt features serene landscapes and a strong connection to nature, with landmarks like the Bell Tower and Ruins of Alph.\p")
}

text BlackVoid_Text_Comment_Hoenn {
    format("A tropical region with a variety of climates, Hoenn is characterized by its islands, rainforests, and volcanoes.\pIts unique terrain promotes environmental themes, and it boasts legendary Pokémon tied to land, sea, and sky.\p")
}

